  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WTC : Recruitment Day is a very short side-story comedy/drama interactive visual novel, based on the main \"Welcome To... Chichester\" series, and set in a semi-fictional world of secret organisations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is self-contained, and so reading other episodes is not a requirement to enjoy this game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After Grendel Jinx is mugged, she chases after the thief, determined to retrieve her possessions - and also recruit the person responsible.  For once, Grendel's lack of attention to security protocols at \"The Council Of The Unseen\" may have prevented further problems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grendel Jinx is voiced by \"Sarah\" </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two different endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Short, two chapter story (approx. around 30 minutes to complete) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The '<i>Self-Expanding Frying Pan</i>' is back ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spanish translation by Daynel Chavez (@imqu4d)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Japanese translation by Translator GORO=chan (@gorochantransl1)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rating : Off-screen violence.  Some adult dialogue </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/2590e6d6272d33b751f51f33fcf87783.avif?t=1760132162\" width=233 height=338 /></span>Grendel Jinx and her mother.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/32193debd332cbebc65d1cfdb6d663ee.avif?t=1760132162\" width=233 height=338 /></span>Lorinda Ella and The Boss</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WTC : Recruitment Day is a very short side-story comedy/drama interactive visual novel, based on the main \"Welcome To... Chichester\" series, and set in a semi-fictional world of secret organisations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is self-contained, and so reading other episodes is not a requirement to enjoy this game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/3019051846d4e86dcff2f5a6361bc33c.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After Grendel Jinx is mugged, she chases after the thief, determined to retrieve her possessions - and also recruit the person responsible.  For once, Grendel's lack of attention to security protocols at \"The Council Of The Unseen\" may have prevented further problems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/5f104b6467c0689cb5d8207659e502ee.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grendel Jinx is voiced by \"Sarah\" </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two different endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Short, two chapter story (approx. around 30 minutes to complete) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The '<i>Self-Expanding Frying Pan</i>' is back ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spanish translation by Daynel Chavez (@imqu4d)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Japanese translation by Translator GORO=chan (@gorochantransl1)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rating : Off-screen violence.  Some adult dialogue </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.webp?t=1760132162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras_big/1b473a6885e888a8efde60b8440d3455.avif?t=1760132162 width=800 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/2590e6d6272d33b751f51f33fcf87783.avif?t=1760132162\" width=233 height=338 /></span>Grendel Jinx and her mother.     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1916660/extras/32193debd332cbebc65d1cfdb6d663ee.avif?t=1760132162\" width=233 height=338 /></span>Lorinda Ella and The Boss</p>",
